block.rankine.ultra_high_refractory_bric: Ultra High Refractory Bricks Vertical Slab
enchantment.rankine.puncture.desc: Deals extra armor-piercing damage on direct attacks.
enchantment.rankine.blast.desc: Causes the hammer to explode blocks in a radius.
enchantment.rankine.atomize.desc: Rolls specific outputs again if they were missed on the first roll when crushing.
enchantment.rankine.lightning_aspect.des: Causes lightning to strike when attacking targets.
enchantment.rankine.swing.desc: Decreases the cooldown of effects caused by swinging the hammer by 15% (additive).
enchantment.rankine.excavate.desc: Increases the number of blocks broken by swinging the hammer.
enchantment.rankine.daze.desc: Applies slow on targets. Effect enhanced on perfect swing.
enchantment.rankine.gas_protection.desc: Protects from harmful effects of gases.
enchantment.rankine.quake.desc: Increases mining speed based on depth.
enchantment.rankine.foraging.desc: Adds chance to gain various items from digging in dirt.
enchantment.rankine.antiquated.desc: Increases the luck stat while held in the main hand or off hand.
enchantment.rankine.cleanse.desc: Deals extra damage based on the number of potion effects the target has.
enchantment.rankine.endpoint.desc: Teleports the user to where the spear lands. Levels reduce the amount of damage taken.
enchantment.rankine.withering_curse.desc: Taking damage (that isn't wither or magic related) causes you to receive the Wither effect for a short duration.
enchantment.rankine.prying.desc: On hit, has a chance to cause the target to drop their held item. Chance is determined by rarity of the item.
jei.description.crushing_basic: Can be obtained by crushing ores using a machine or a Bronze Hammer.
death.attack.suffocating.player: %1$s suffocated in a gas cloud whilst trying to escape %2$s
enchantment.rankine.retrieval.desc: Can harvest any block provided its harvest level matches or is less than the crowbar's harvest level. Cannot harvest blocks in #rankine:crowbar_resistant.
enchantment.rankine.fulcrum.desc: When hitting a block that cannot be harvested, accelerate your current motion.
enchantment.rankine.leverage.desc: Deal increased damage to entities based on their size.
enchantment.rankine.lift.desc: When right-clicking a block in the air, bring yourself to the top of the block if there is no obstruction.
enchantment.rankine.retaliate.desc: On successful parry, deal the damage you would have taken back to the enemy.
enchantment.rankine.retreat.desc: On successful parry, turn invisible for a brief amount of time.
enchantment.rankine.backstab.desc: Deals a multiplier of your damage when hitting an enemy on their back.
enchantment.rankine.poison_aspect.desc: Applies a Poison or Weakness effect on enemies (depending on type) for a short duration.
enchantment.rankine.grafting.desc: Guarantees a sapling drop from leaves.
rankine.advancements.story.root.title: Project Rankine
rankine.advancements.story.root.descript: Begin delving into the changed world
rankine.advancements.story.gather_rope.d: Gather rope by obtaining a flint knife and harvesting grass
rankine.advancements.story.get_flint_axe: Make a Flint Handaxe to harvest wood early and more easily
rankine.advancements.story.make_charcoal: Make a Charcoal Pit to help alleviate early fuel requirements and make large batches of charcoal
rankine.advancements.story.get_flint_too: Construct a Flint Pickaxe to begin mining
rankine.advancements.story.get_stone_ham: Construct a Stone Hammer to crush blocks for different products, including those to make cobblestone
rankine.advancements.story.get_flint_spe: Make a throwable Flint Spear to protect yourself
rankine.advancements.story.make_refracto: Make Refractory Brick by finding clay and using mortar
rankine.advancements.story.make_alloy_fu: Make an Alloy Furnace by using sheetmetal and refractory bricks
rankine.advancements.story.make_template: Make an Alloy Template Table to automate the creation of alloys
rankine.advancements.story.make_evaporat: Construct an Evaporation Tower to generate resources from water in different biomes
rankine.advancements.story.make_coal_for: Make a Coal Forge to make alloy tools
rankine.advancements.story.get_bronze_to: Make a Bronze, Rose Gold, or Pewter Hammer to begin crushing ores
rankine.advancements.story.make_template: Make templates to construct alloy tools at the coal forge
rankine.advancements.story.make_blast_fu: Make a Blast Furnace to begin smelting more complex ores
rankine.advancements.story.find_meteorit: Find a meteorite and crush the ore in it to get meteoric iron
rankine.advancements.story.find_ironston: Find ironstone under the sands of a desert or mesa
rankine.advancements.story.make_cast_iro: Make cast iron alloy by using a form of carbon and pig iron
rankine.advancements.story.make_tree_tap: Make a tree tap to begin extracting liquids from trees
Heal some minor damage with a bandage
rankine.advancements.story.make_trampoli: Make a trampoline to launch high into the air
rankine.advancements.story.make_herbicid: Produce herbicide from juglone to clear patches of grass and other plants
rankine.advancements.story.make_piston_c: Make a piston crusher to automate crushing
rankine.advancements.story.make_quartz.d: Find or make quartz by crushing stones
rankine.advancements.story.make_glass_cu: Make a glass cutter to minimize losses
rankine.advancements.story.make_pig_iron: Make pig iron by smelting an iron ingot
rankine.advancements.story.make_quicklim: Produce quicklime from combusting limestone with the beehive oven
rankine.advancements.story.make_roman_co: Make roman concrete from pozzolanic mortar
rankine.advancements.story.make_magnesia: Make magnesia from cooking a magnesite block with the beehive oven
rankine.advancements.story.make_coke.tit: I cant believe it's not Coal!
rankine.advancements.story.make_coke.des: Use a beehive oven to produce coke from bituminous and sub-bituminous coal blocks
rankine.advancements.story.make_wrought_: Make Wrought Iron by crushing bloom iron made from the Beehive Oven
rankine.advancements.story.make_crucible: Construct a crucible to make steel
rankine.advancements.story.make_steel_al: Make Steel Alloy by using the Crucible or the Induction Furnace
rankine.advancements.story.make_brigandi: Make a full set of Brigandine Armor
rankine.advancements.story.make_inductio: Make an Induction Furnace for more advanced alloys
rankine.advancements.story.make_steel_go: Make a Steel Gold Pan to sieve alluvium and black sand
rankine.advancements.story.make_nickel_s: Make every available type of Nickel Superalloy tool
rankine.advancements.story.make_stainles: Make every available type of Stainless Steel tool
rankine.advancements.story.make_tungsten: Make every available type of Tungsten Heavy Alloy tool
rankine.advancements.story.make_cobalt_s: Make every available type of Cobalt Superalloy tool
rankine.advancements.story.make_element_: Create an Element Transmuter, a substance from otherworldly materials that can extract elements
rankine.advancements.story.make_power_ce: Make any power cell for use in advanced machines
rankine.advancements.story.make_electrom: Make any type of Electromagnet Block
rankine.advancements.story.make_gyratory: Make a Gyratory Crusher to automate crushing further
rankine.advancements.story.make_rankine_: Make a Rankine Box to transmute elements
rankine.advancements.story.make_laser_qu: Construct a Laser Quarry to mine out large chunks of the world
rankine.advancements.story.make_thorium_: Make Thorium Arrows to control the power of lightning with your bow
rankine.advancements.story.support.title: We support Patchouli and JEI!
rankine.advancements.story.support.descr: Be sure to download these mods if you want more information!
rankine.advancements.challenges.root.des: Complete your understanding of the changed world
rankine.advancements.challenges.rock_col: Collect all the new types of rocks
rankine.advancements.challenges.element_: Collect every element in the Periodic Table
rankine.advancements.challenges.make_all: Make every type of Power Cell
rankine.advancements.challenges.pendant_: Make every type of Colored Gold Pendant
rankine.advancements.story.make_element_: Use a device to examine element properties
rankine.advancements.challenges.alloy_co: Create all of the different types of alloys
rankine.advancements.challenges.bronze_h: Make a Bronze Pickaxe with a Harvest Level of 2 (or Invar equivalent)
rankine.advancements.challenges.pewter_e: Make a Pewter Tool with an Enchantability greater than or equal to 14
rankine.advancements.challenges.colored_: Make a Colored Gold tool using Netherite instead of Gold
rankine.advancements.challenges.find_met: Find all the forms of meteoric iron
rankine.advancements.challenges.geode_co: Find all of the different types of geodes
